casebody.data:
No. 638,

Misc.

Foster v. California. Thomas C. Lynch, Attorney General of California, and Edward A. Hinz, Jr., and Charles P. Just, Deputy Attorneys General, for respondent.

Ct. App. Cal., 5th App. Dist. Motion for leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted. Certiorari granted limited to question whether the conduct of the police lineup resulted in a violation of petitioner’s constitutional rights. Case transferred to appellate docket.
